        <td bgColor="black"><textarea cols="45" name="Message" rows="6" wrap="VIRTUAL">[quote]
I think everything is right on target, except the pet thing.

IMO, I don't think the necro is *necessarily* a pet class.  I haven't used a pet while soloing in over a month, and I have a lvl 51 necro friend still using the 34 pet when he uses one.  

And about the hp thing..I agree 100% that the 59 pet should be way WAY increased.  The 53 and 56 pet I would agree if they were *warriors*, but they are a rogue and a monk.  Those two classes don't have the same number of HPs as a warrior, and while I think they should be increased, not necessarily on the same proportion as you propose.  

Everything else I agree with totally...just don't think so much importance should be placeed on pets, they aren't that necessarily when you're creative.

Spell drops still suck ass

 
[/quote]</textarea><br>
        

