issue) or taps weren't working.  This also wasn't directed at Verant.  I do not believe they read this board anymore first of all considering their silence in even acknowledging the taps were broken.  Secondly, as stated above, we are a minority of players and if they want to make money they please the majority first (Safehouse.)  Thats unfortunate but just the way it is.</P><P>Daedrea Darksoul</font></td>
